(68, 'S0068', 'Truyen ngon tinh - Giac mo Trung Quoc', 'Phuc Luu Minh', 2, 'MintRight Inc', 'China Dream is the first book openly declared that China will replace the US as world leader, became leader country, the most prosperous nation.', 'cuốn', 'sach_S0068.jpg', 100, 123000.00, 35.00, 1, 1, '2026-03-14 17:39:05'),
