(79, 'S0079', 'The Brothers Karamazov', 'F M Dostoevsky', 2, 'NXB Tổng hợp', 'Vietnamese edition of the great Russian literary fiction by Fyodor Dostoevsky. Translated from the original Russian text, by Pham Manh Hung.', 'cuốn', 'sach_S0079.jpg', 100, 122000.00, 34.00, 1, 1, '2026-03-14 17:39:05'),
