(484, 'S0484', 'Dictionnaire FRANÇAIS - VIETNAMIEN En images: Từ điển PHÁP - VIỆT bằng hình (theo chủ đề)', 'Phương Dung,  Nguyễn Thức Thành Tín', 6, 'Trí Tuệ', 'Avant-propos Félicitations ! Vous avez entre vos mains le Dictionnaire français-vietnamien en images. Cet ouvrage constitue une ressource précieuse pour enrichir et perfectionner votre vocabulaire français. Élaboré avec soin, il comprend 305 pages, réparties en 142 thèmes et agrémentées de nombreuses illustrations, facilitant ainsi l’apprentissage et la mémorisation du vocabulaire. Destiné tant aux adultes qu’aux enfants, ce dictionnaire mise sur une approche visuelle innovante. En associant chaque mot à une image, il crée des liens cognitifs forts et durables, vous permettant de retenir le vocabulaire de manière naturelle et de l’utiliser avec assurance dans la vie quotidienne. Cette méthode visuelle vous aide à forger des connexions solides dans votre esprit, favorisant une mémorisation rapide et efficace. Conçu avec des thèmes indépendants, ce livre vous permet d’aborder les sujets dans l’ordre de votre choix. Néanmoins, nous vous encourageons à consacrer du temps à l’étude de chaqu', 'cuốn', 'sach_S0484.jpg', 100, 89000.00, 22.00, 1, 1, '2026-03-14 18:05:11'),
(485, 'S0485', 'Vietnamese - English dictionary : Từ điển Việt Anh', 'Tạ Văn Hùng,  Huy Khang', 6, 'Trí Tuệ', 'The dictionary includes 80000 entries, all of which have English comparisons or explanations and examples to illustrate how to use words to help readers easily refer to, visualize and relate to specific contexts. The terms are compared according to the principle of brevity, clarity or clear and simple explanations. The book is for English learners and foreigners who are learning Vietnamese. Tra cứu từ vựng Việt - Anh trong nhiều lĩnh vực, tên các quốc gia, và đặc biệt trong các lĩnh vực về máy tính, kiến trúc và y học. Quyển sách phù hợp với những người Việt đang sống và làm việc ở nước ngoài muốn tra cứu tài liệu. If you want the PDF file to print the book or use it for commercial purposes, please contact: Bạn đọc có nhu cầu cần file để in sách hoặc sử dụng với mục đích thương mại, xin vui lòng liên hệ: Email: taquanghuy2001@yahoo.com hoặc congtytritue_79@yahoo.com.vn Zalo: (84)0909081183 Điện thoại (Tel): (84)0904547036 Trí Tuệ', 'cuốn', 'sach_S0485.jpg', 100, 102000.00, 24.00, 1, 1, '2026-03-14 18:05:11'),
(486, 'S0486', 'Vietnamese-English Dictionary', 'Nhiều tác giả', 6, 'NXB Tổng hợp', '', 'cuốn', 'sach_S0486.jpg', 100, 108000.00, 30.00, 1, 1, '2026-03-14 18:05:11'),
(487, 'S0487', 'Nam\'s River Reveries', 'Duc Thien', 6, 'Duc Thien', 'In the enchanting folds of a Vietnamese village where the Red River\'s gentle flow cradles tales of wonder and whimsy, Nam\'s River Reveries brings together 20 bilingual stories (in Vietnamese and English) from Nam\'s latest escapades, blending the thrill of discovery with the quiet beauty of everyday lessons. From the intrigue of a mysterious gift sprouting ancient secrets to the chaos of a canceled flight turning into unexpected adventures, and from the hush of a no-coffee day to the glow of a lantern-lit festival, these narratives illuminate themes of curiosity, resilience, and the magic hidden in mishaps. Illustrated with Nam\'s charming, childlike notebook sketches, each story captures the rhythm of rural life-rainy afternoons chasing paper kites, early market barters under dawn mist, and starlit nights pondering the longest day. Inspired by Vietnam\'s vibrant cultural tapestry, this volume invites young readers and their families to revel in Nam\'s innocent worldview, where a tangled h', 'cuốn', 'sach_S0487.jpg', 100, 133000.00, 29.00, 1, 1, '2026-03-14 18:05:11'),
